# Inbox modal with items
Set Shell "bash"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 16
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set TypingSpeed 0

Type "wolfcastle"
Enter
Sleep 8s

# Open inbox modal
Type "i"
Sleep 1s

Screenshot tui-inbox-modal.png
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
